# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:14
translate portuguese adrian10_7b84c3bc:

    # "My phone buzzes in my pocket. Looks like Adrian is calling."
    "O meu telemóvel vibra no bolso. Parece que é a Adrian a ligar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:18
translate portuguese adrian10_4f07aa53:

    # pc "Hey, Adrian."
    pc "Olá, Adrian."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:19
translate portuguese adrian10_c932651c:

    # gg "Hey, [pcname]. You busy? Got time to listen to me bitch a little?"
    gg "Olá, [pcname]. Estás ocupada? Tens tempo para me ouvires queixar-me um pouco?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:20
translate portuguese adrian10_82701f42:

    # pc "Sure, what's up?"
    pc "Claro, o que se passa?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:24
translate portuguese adrian10_610c0cf9:

    # gg "I've been thinking a lot about the future. What I want to do after college and everything."
    gg "Tenho pensado muito no futuro. No que quero fazer depois da faculdade e tudo mais."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:25
translate portuguese adrian10_fa6e4cda:

    # gg "Right now, I'm majoring in computer programming. That's what I thought I wanted to do. Become a programmer of some sort, maybe work on a game or something?"
    gg "Neste momento, estou a tirar a licenciatura em programação informática. Era isso que eu achava que queria fazer. Tornar-me programador de algum tipo, talvez trabalhar num jogo ou algo assim?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:26
translate portuguese adrian10_fc672958:

    # gg "But the more I've done it, the more I think it's not for me. I don't really enjoy the coding, the numbers and all that."
    gg "Mas quanto mais faço isto, mais acho que não é para mim. Não gosto muito de programar, dos números e tudo isso."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:27
translate portuguese adrian10_1e97fd27:

    # gg "So I've been thinking about changing up my major and maybe trying something different."
    gg "Por isso, tenho pensado em mudar de curso e talvez experimentar algo diferente."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:28
translate portuguese adrian10_0c391334:

    # pc "Like what?"
    pc "Como o quê?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:30
translate portuguese adrian10_f79f2661:

    # gg "So I had this idea about opening up a business."
    gg "Tive a ideia de abrir um negócio."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:31
translate portuguese adrian10_4d4cf96f:

    # pc "Oh, really?"
    pc "A sério?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:32
translate portuguese adrian10_b57bf29b:

    # gg "Yeah! So, it would be like an arcade, but a little different."
    gg "Sim! Seria tipo um salão de jogos, mas um pouco diferente."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:33
translate portuguese adrian10_818c3b19:

    # gg "It would have the open arcade where the cabinets are and you can pay a flat fee to go in and play the machines as much as you want."
    gg "Teria a área aberta onde estão as máquinas e pagavas uma taxa fixa para entrar e jogar o quanto quisesses."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:34
translate portuguese adrian10_427a9d8b:

    # gg "But it would also have private booths that you could rent that have like couches and a big television and you could play console games on it. Like old stuff, or modern stuff. And you rent the booths by the hour or something."
    gg "Mas também teria cabines privadas que se poderiam alugar, com sofás e uma televisão grande, onde se poderia jogar jogos de consola. Coisas antigas ou modernas. E alugava-se as cabines por hora ou algo do género."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:35
translate portuguese adrian10_39c37c49:

    # gg "And you could order food and drinks and stuff that servers would bring to your booth."
    gg "E podia-se pedir comida, bebidas e outras coisas que os empregados de mesa levariam até à cabine."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:36
translate portuguese adrian10_61c01a73:

    # pc "Sounds like you've been thinking about this for a while."
    pc "Parece que já pensas nisto há algum tempo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:38
translate portuguese adrian10_7153901f:

    # gg "I have! It's like my dream business."
    gg "Penso mesmo! É tipo o negócio dos meus sonhos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:39
translate portuguese adrian10_10cc920d:

    # gg "I thought that I wanted to {i}make{/i} games, but now I think maybe I just like playing them and introducing other people to them."
    gg "Eu pensava que queria {i}criar{/i} jogos, mas agora acho que talvez só goste de jogá-los e de os apresentar a outras pessoas."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:41
translate portuguese adrian10_d7eeeca5:

    # gg "So what do you think? Do you think I should go for it, or should I stick with the programming?"
    gg "Então, o que achas? Achas que devo avançar com isto, ou devo continuar com a programação?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:42
translate portuguese adrian10_cd4d62c9:

    # gg "Opening a business is risky. A computer programming degree would pretty much guarantee me a job somewhere. More than a business degree would, I think."
    gg "Abrir um negócio é arriscado. Uma licenciatura em programação informática garantir-me-ia praticamente um emprego em algum lugar. Mais do que uma licenciatura em gestão, acho eu."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:43
translate portuguese adrian10_6b813540:

    # gg "But having my own business like that sounds amazing. I think I'd love it, and I'd be good at it."
    gg "Mas ter o meu próprio negócio assim parece incrível. Acho que iria adorar e que seria boa nisso."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:48
translate portuguese adrian10_1cd10274:

    # gg "Yeah?"
    gg "A sério?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:49
translate portuguese adrian10_87461b0f:

    # pc "Yeah! You should do whatever you think is going to make you happiest."
    pc "Sim! Deves fazer o que achares que te vai fazer mais feliz."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:50
translate portuguese adrian10_4152e0c4:

    # gg "Wow, I'm so happy to have your support. I think so too. It just feels good to talk to somebody about it who doesn't think it's just a silly idea."
    gg "Uau, estou tão feliz por ter o teu apoio. Também acho isso. É tão bom falar com alguém sobre isto que não acha que é apenas uma ideia tola."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:51
translate portuguese adrian10_a694f75e:

    # pc "No I don't think it's silly at all. Sounds really cool."
    pc "Não, não acho nada que seja tolo. Parece mesmo fixe."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:53
translate portuguese adrian10_8531f092:

    # gg "Awesome. I guess I'll talk to the counselor and have her switch up my degree plan for next semester."
    gg "Fantástico. Acho que vou falar com a orientadora e pedir-lhe para alterar o meu plano de estudos para o próximo semestre."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:54
translate portuguese adrian10_54287c82:

    # gg "And I'll start looking more into what would be required for me to open a business like that."
    gg "E vou começar a investigar melhor o que seria necessário para abrir um negócio assim."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:55
translate portuguese adrian10_aa87f601:

    # gg "Oh man, I'm so fucking excited!"
    gg "Caramba, estou tão entusiasmada!"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:56
translate portuguese adrian10_87a3e492:

    # pc "Me too! It sounds so cool!"
    pc "Eu também! Parece tão fixe!"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:58
translate portuguese adrian10_651cac03:

    # gg "You're the best. Seriously. Thank you."
    gg "És o melhor. A sério. Obrigada."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:59
translate portuguese adrian10_1f5cd361:

    # pc "Any time. I'm here for you."
    pc "Sempre à disposição. Estou aqui para te apoiar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:60
translate portuguese adrian10_cc9d651b:

    # gg "I'll keep you updated."
    gg "Vou manter-te a par."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:63
translate portuguese adrian10_9b8e5bbe:

    # gg "You think so?"
    gg "Achas mesmo?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:64
translate portuguese adrian10_ce11aceb:

    # pc "Yeah - better to have that guarantee. If you started a business and it failed, what would you do then?"
    pc "Sim – é melhor ter essa garantia. Se abrisses um negócio e ele falhasse, o que farias então?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:65
translate portuguese adrian10_99766421:

    # gg "I'd find something else to do."
    gg "Encontraria outra coisa para fazer."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:66
translate portuguese adrian10_fddb6cee:

    # pc "Well, I think you should stick with programming. You might grow to like it more and it's going to pay better, I'm sure."
    pc "Bem, acho que devias continuar com a programação. Podes acabar por gostar mais e vai render melhor, tenho a certeza."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:67
translate portuguese adrian10_b4f625aa:

    # gg "Man, that's a bummer. I was really hoping to have your support here."
    gg "Caramba, que chatice. Estava mesmo à espera de ter o teu apoio nisto."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:68
translate portuguese adrian10_21467e2b:

    # gg "I mean, I'm going to do whatever the fuck I want to do, either way, but it would be nice if you were behind me on it."
    gg "Quer dizer, vou fazer o que me der na foda, de qualquer maneira, mas seria bom se me apoiasses nisto."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:69
translate portuguese adrian10_1dcb80a3:

    # pc "It's not that I'm not behind you, I just think that changing your major and opening a business is a bad idea."
    pc "Não é que não te apoie, só acho que mudar de curso e abrir um negócio é uma má ideia."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:70
translate portuguese adrian10_fbd4b012:

    # gg "Well, okay. Still a bummer."
    gg "Bem, tudo bem. Continua a ser uma chatice."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:71
translate portuguese adrian10_db859f40:

    # gg "I'm going to get some sleep. I'll talk to you later, [pcname]."
    gg "Vou dormir um pouco. Falo contigo mais tarde, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:72
translate portuguese adrian10_0c692dc8:

    # pc "All right. Good night, Adrian."
    pc "Tudo bem. Boa noite, Adrian."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian10.rpy:75
translate portuguese adrian10_a6fae33b:

    # "We hang up and I get ready to go to bed."
    "Desligamos e eu preparo-me para ir para a cama."

